CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Willis Towers Watson Plc is registered with the U.S. Security and Exchange Commission and incorporated in the state of Ireland. Willis Towers Watson Plc is primarely in the business of insurance agents brokers & services. For financial reporting, their fiscal year ends on December 31st. This page includes all SEC registration details as well as a list of all documents (S-1, Prospectus, Current Reports, 8-K, 10K, Annual Reports) filed by Willis Towers Watson Plc. In January 2016, Towers Watson and Willis Group merged to form Willis Towers Watson, a global advisory, insurance brokerage, and solutions company. The company operates in four business segments: corporate risk and brokerage; benefits delivery and administration; human capital and benefits; and investment, risk, and reinsurance.
